  "body": "# Bug Report\n\n## Problem\nSometimes Status app shows constant syncing bar, however internet connection is stable.\nReported by @jarradh, creating an issue to keep track on it.\n\n#### Expected behavior\nStatus connected, no connectivity bar is shown\n\n#### Actual behavior\n> Status continually syncing \n\n### Reproduction\n\n[comment]: # (Describe how we can replicate the bug step by step.)\n\n> - Open Status\n> - Watch Status sync for longer than 20 seconds sometimes new messages come through but still acts as if syncing \n> - Status continually syncing \n\n### Additional Information\n----------------------------------------\nApp version: 1.8.0 (20201019145001)\nOS: android\nNode version: StatusIM/v0.62.11/android-arm64/go1.14.7\nMailserver: mail-02.ac-cn-hongkong-c.eth.prod\n\n#### Logs\n\n28/10/20:\n[Status-debug-logs.zip](https://github.com/status-im/status-react/files/5473701/Status-debug-logs.zip)\n\n02/11/20:\n[Status-debug-logs.zip](https://github.com/status-im/status-react/files/5473699/Status-debug-logs.zip)",
